參考https://medium.com/soulweb-academy/easily-build-and-publish-a-react-typescript-component-library-package-to-npm-using-storybook-and-4836d4f700b6

1.設置 storybook

npx create-react-app storybook-date --template typescript
cd storybook-date
npx storybook@latest init

2.移除預設 stroybook
rm -rf src/stories/*
mkdir src/components

3.設置依賴項
dependencies 的內容都要搬到 devDependencies
rm -rf package-lock.json
npm install

4.建立一個組件
***待開發***

5.執行storybook查看
npm run storybook

6.設置對等依賴項，讓客戶可以用到我們的庫
